== 早年生活 ==
蘇菲亞在1984年12月6日出生於[[丹德呂德市|丹德呂德市]]丹德呂德醫院，父親是[[丹麥人|丹麥人]]，母親是[[瑞典人|瑞典人]]。幼時在[[泰比|泰比]]度過，她在6歲時搬到{{link-en|艾爾夫達倫|Älvdalen}}<ref name=expressen2>{{cite news |title=Det här är Sofia - lär känna prinsens flickvän |first=Malin |last=Forsberg |url=http://www.expressen.se/noje/extra/1.1856264/det-har-ar-sofia-lar-kanna-prinsens-flickvan |newspaper=[[Expressen|Expressen]] |date=2010-01-24 |language=sv |accessdate=2011-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100504043355/http://www.expressen.se/noje/extra/1.1856264/det-har-ar-sofia-lar-kanna-prinsens-flickvan |archive-date=2010-05-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dt.se/dalarna/alvdalen/prinsen-ofta-pa-besok-i-alvdalen|title=Prinsen ofta på besök i Älvdalen|work=dt.se|accessdate=2015-06-11|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626134623/http://www.dt.se/dalarna/alvdalen/prinsen-ofta-pa-besok-i-alvdalen|dead-url=no}}</ref>，上有名叫莎拉和琳娜的兩個姊姊<ref name="USMagWedding">{{Cite web|title = Sofia Hellqvist and Prince Carl Philip of Sweden marry in spectacular wedding ceremony|url = http://us.hellomagazine.com/royalty/2015061325605/sofia-hellqvist-prince-carl-philip-marry/|website = hellomagazine.com|accessdate = 2015-06-13|first = hellomagazine.com|last = S.A.|date = 2015-06-13|archive-date = 2018-07-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180710102844/https://us.hellomagazine.com/royalty/2015061325605/sofia-hellqvist-prince-carl-philip-marry/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。20歲時，曾為了瑞典的一家{{link-en|男性雜誌列表|List of men's magazines|男性雜誌}}Slitz拍攝了上半身僅用[[蟒蛇|蟒蛇]]遮蔽，下半身著[[比基尼泳衣|比基尼]]的照片<ref name=telegraph>{{cite news |title=Swedish prince has relationship with glamour model |first=Nick |last=Squires |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/sweden/7568005/Swedish-prince-has-relationship-with-glamour-model.html |newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |date=2010-04-08 |accessdate=2011-06-04 |archive-date=2011-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111005154024/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/sweden/7568005/Swedish-prince-has-relationship-with-glamour-model.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2004年，她被讀者票選為Slitz女郎<ref name=expressen3>{{cite news |title=Sofia Hellqvist har vikt ut sig i Slitz |first=Johan T |last=Lindwall |url=http://www.expressen.se/Nyheter/1.1843310/sofia-hellqvist-har-vikt-ut-sig-i-slitz |newspaper=[[Expressen|Expressen]] |date=2010-01-13 |language=sv |accessdate=2011-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110828103541/http://www.expressen.se/Nyheter/1.1843310/sofia-hellqvist-har-vikt-ut-sig-i-slitz |archive-date=2011-08-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2010年，當蘇菲亞和王子的戀情被揭露時，瑞典的一家報紙《{{link-en|快報 (瑞典)|Expressen|快報}}》再次刊登了這張照片<ref name=expressen4>{{cite news |title=Bilderna Silvia knappast sett på prinsens nya romans |first=Nathalie |last=Joo |url=http://www.expressen.se/nyheter/1.1844260/bilderna-silvia-knappast-sett-pa-prinsens-nya-romans |newspaper=[[Expressen|Expressen]] |date=2010-01-14 |language=sv |accessdate=2011-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607042240/http://www.expressen.se/nyheter/1.1844260/bilderna-silvia-knappast-sett-pa-prinsens-nya-romans |archive-date=2011-06-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

在2004年被選為雜誌女郎後，{{link-en|TV4 (瑞典)|TV4 (Sweden)|TV4}}電視台的《{{link-en|樂園旅館|Paradise Hotel}}》（Paradise Hotel）[[真人實境秀|真人實境秀]]節目提供了演出機會<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thelocal.se/20140627/swedish-prince-carl-philip-to-marry|title=Swedish prince to marry 'Paradise Hotel' girlfriend|publisher=|accessdate=2015-06-11|archive-date=2015-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150613105343/http://www.thelocal.se/20140627/swedish-prince-carl-philip-to-marry|dead-url=no}}</ref>， 她接下了工作，並且留到最後<ref name=expressen4 />。在演出期間，她曾與另一位參賽者Olinda Castielle有過公開的爭執
<ref name=expressen5>{{cite news |title=Hatattacker mot Paradise -Olinda |first1=Anja |last1=Edvardsson |first2=Mats |last2=Pettersson |url=http://www.expressen.se/noje/1.186275/hatattacker-mot-paradise-olinda |newspaper=[[Expressen|Expressen]] |date=2005-03-18 |language=sv |accessdate=2011-06-04 }}{{Dead link|date=2018年9月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>
<ref name=aftonbladet2>{{cite news |title=Här blir Olinda mobbad |first=Karin |last=Wik |url=http://www.aftonbladet.se/nojesbladet/tv/dokusapa/article274745.ab |newspaper=[[Aftonbladet|Aftonbladet]] |date=2005-03-25 |language=sv |accessdate=2011-06-04 |archive-date=2012-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019190844/http://www.aftonbladet.se/nojesbladet/tv/dokusapa/article274745.ab |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2005年<ref name=abc>{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-06-14/swedish-prince-weds-former-glamour-model/6544390|title=Swedish prince weds Sofia Hellqvist, commoner and former glamour model|date=2015-06-13|accessdate=2015-06-13|author=Reuters|archive-date=2015-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614081314/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-06-14/swedish-prince-weds-former-glamour-model/6544390|dead-url=no}}</ref>，她搬到[[紐約|紐約]]，在英語與商學院（Institute of English and Business）學習[[會計|會計]]與電腦應用，專攻為業務發展（Business Development）。此外，她也曾在[[斯德哥爾摩大學|斯德哥爾摩大學]]學習了其他課程，例如[[全球倫理|全球倫理]]（global ethics）、兒童與青少年研究、兒童溝通（children's communication），與實踐《聯合國兒童權利公約》（UN Convention on the Rights of the Child）等<ref>{{cite web|title=Sofia Hellqvist Info|url=http://www.kungahuset.se/download/18.44b9de9714527ae8f1d29dc3/1403879674678/CV+SH+eng.pdf|accessdate=2015-06-14|archive-date=2015-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150205085104/http://www.kungahuset.se/download/18.44b9de9714527ae8f1d29dc3/1403879674678/CV+SH+eng.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>；她也在[[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]開設了自己的[[瑜珈|瑜珈]]中心<ref name=expressen4 />。

她曾自爆在[[拉斯維加斯|拉斯維加斯]]參觀期間，與[[美國|美國]]的[[色情|色情]]片女星[[珍娜·詹姆森|珍娜·詹姆森]]熱吻，因而上了頭條新聞<ref name=aftonbladet4>{{cite news |title=Kysstes med porrstjärnan |first=Pontus |last=Hammarlund |url=http://www.aftonbladet.se/nojesbladet/tv/dokusapa/article12100027.ab |newspaper=[[Aftonbladet|Aftonbladet]] |date=2005-04-17 |language=sv |accessdate=2011-06-04 |archive-date=2011-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111124014040/http://www.aftonbladet.se/nojesbladet/tv/dokusapa/article12100027.ab |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://metro.co.uk/2014/10/07/sofia-hellqvist-is-the-former-glamour-model-about-to-marry-a-swedish-prince-4896110/|title=Sofia Hellqvist is the former glamour model about to marry a Swedish prince - Metro News|work=Metro|accessdate=2015-06-11|archive-date=2015-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614040116/http://metro.co.uk/2014/10/07/sofia-hellqvist-is-the-former-glamour-model-about-to-marry-a-swedish-prince-4896110/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

之後，她回到[[斯德哥尔摩|斯德哥尔摩]]繼續求學，同時擔任[[服務生|服務生]]與[[魅力攝影|魅力攝影]][[模特兒|模特兒]]的[[兼職|兼職]]
<ref name=expressen3/>。2010年，她與朋友共同創設了「{{link-sv|遊樂場計畫|Project Playground}}」（Project Playground）的慈善組織。該組織在[[南非|南非]]協助弱勢兒童<ref name=abc/>。

== 與王子的關係 ==
[[Image:Prince_Carl_Philip_and_Princess_Sofia-2.jpg|220px]]

2010年4月，[[英國|英國]]《[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]》爆料，王子結交的新歡蘇菲亞，曾為半裸照的模特兒，與真人實境秀的參賽者；報導並稱，王宮因為感到尷尬，被迫採取守勢不予回應<ref name=telegraph />；7月，{{link-sv|瑞典宮廷|Kungliga Hovstaterna}}（職責類似日本[[宮內廳|宮內廳]]）的發言人，宣讀了王子的聲明，從而證實了蘇菲亞與王子的關係<ref>{{cite web|title=Palace confirms Prince Carl Philip's romance after blocking nude photos|url=http://ca.hellomagazine.com/royalty/201007303945/prince-carl-philip/sofia-hellqvist/romance-confirmed/|accessdate=2015-02-05|archive-date=2015-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150205182721/http://ca.hellomagazine.com/royalty/201007303945/prince-carl-philip/sofia-hellqvist/romance-confirmed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年4月，又有報導稱兩人已搬到瑞典[[動物園島|動物園島]]的一座私人莊園中[[同居|同居]]<ref name=posh24>{{cite news |title=Prins Carl Philip & Sofia Hellqvist flyttar! |url=http://www.posh24.se/svenska_kandisar/prins_carl_philip_sofia_hellqvist_flyttar |work=Posh24.se |date=2011-04-15 |language=sv |accessdate=2011-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110418062848/http://www.posh24.se/svenska_kandisar/prins_carl_philip_sofia_hellqvist_flyttar |archive-date=2011-04-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> ；同年6月，再由宮證實此事<ref name=svenskdam>{{cite news |title=Carl Philip och Sofia nu sambor – officiellt |first=Åsa |last=Bönnelyche |url=http://svenskdam.se/2011/06/carl-philip-och-sofia-nu-sambor-officiellt/ |newspaper=Svensk Damtidning |date=2011-06-10 |language=sv |accessdate=2011-06-12 |archive-date=2011-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110612041055/http://svenskdam.se/2011/06/carl-philip-och-sofia-nu-sambor-officiellt/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年6月27日，兩人公開宣布[[訂婚|訂婚]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.closerweekly.com/posts/sweden-s-prince-carl-philip-proposed-to-sofia-hellqvist-s-with-less-than-1-carat-engagement-ring-59433|title=Sweden's Prince Carl Philip Proposed to Sofia Hellqvist With 1 Carat Engagement Ring|date=2015-05-29|work=Closer Weekly|accessdate=2015-06-11|archive-date=2015-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150613124142/http://www.closerweekly.com/posts/sweden-s-prince-carl-philip-proposed-to-sofia-hellqvist-s-with-less-than-1-carat-engagement-ring-59433|dead-url=no}}</ref>；12月，她與未婚夫在{{link-en|諾貝爾獎晚宴|Nobel Banquet}}的舉辦地{{link-en|藍廳|Blue Hall}}中亮相，官方並宣布她將獲得王族的稱號<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.svt.se/nyheter/sverige/modeexperten-om-nobelfestens-snackisar |title=Modeexperten om nobelfestens snackisar |work=svt.se |accessdate=2014-12-25 |archive-date=2014-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141213013731/http://www.svt.se/nyheter/sverige/modeexperten-om-nobelfestens-snackisar |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.expressen.se/nyheter/sa-ska-sofia-sitta-under-nobelfesten/ |title=Så ska Sofia sitta under Nobelfesten |work=Expressen |accessdate=2014-12-25 |archive-date=2014-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141226024423/http://www.expressen.se/nyheter/sa-ska-sofia-sitta-under-nobelfesten/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dn.se/nyheter/sverige/hovet-sofia-blir-prinsessa |title=Hovet: Sofia blir prinsessa |work=dn.se |accessdate=2015-05-20 |archive-date=2015-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150519203911/http://www.dn.se/nyheter/sverige/hovet-sofia-blir-prinsessa/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年6月13日，她與王子在斯德哥爾摩[[結婚|結婚]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Vigsel mellan Prins Carl Philip och fröken Sofia Hellqvist|url=http://www.kungahuset.se/pressrum/pressmeddelanden/2014pressmeddelanden/vigselmellanprinscarlphilipochfrokensofiahellqvist.5.67e94750148caf4ad274b99.html|accessdate=2014-10-23|archive-date=2014-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028115107/http://www.kungahuset.se/pressrum/pressmeddelanden/2014pressmeddelanden/vigselmellanprinscarlphilipochfrokensofiahellqvist.5.67e94750148caf4ad274b99.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.yahoo.com/reality-starlet-wed-prince-swedish-fairytale-092011145.html|title=Reality starlet to wed prince in Swedish fairytale|date=2015-06-11|work=Yahoo News|accessdate=2015-06-11|archive-date=2021-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210505230437/https://news.yahoo.com/reality-starlet-wed-prince-swedish-fairytale-092011145.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Reality starlet weds Swedish prince|url = http://news.yahoo.com/reality-starlet-weds-swedish-prince-101041703.html|accessdate = 2015-06-13|website = Yahoo News|date = 2015-06-13|archive-date = 2020-09-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200920075932/https://news.yahoo.com/reality-starlet-weds-swedish-prince-101041703.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="USMagWedding" />。2016年4月19日,長子[[亞歷山大王子_(瑞典)|亞歷山大]]誕生。2017年8月31日，次子[[加布埃里爾王子_(瑞典)|加布埃里爾]]（Gabriel）於。2020年11月26日，蘇菲亞王妃的[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]病毒检测结果呈阳性<ref>{{cite news |title=瑞典王子菲利普夫妇确诊感染新冠病毒 |url=https://www.sohu.com/a/434591263_267106}}</ref>。

